<HEADLINE> 12 Killed in Kashmir </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
In a major encounter on Sunday night, security forces noticed a
group of four heavily-armed militants trying to infiltrate into
Kashmir from across the border, and in the ensuing exchange of
fire all four were killed, an official spokesman in Kashmir told
the PTI.
</P>
<P>
Two other "Pakistani intruders" were killed when security
forces ambushed a group of militants trying to cross over in the
frontier district of Kupwara in west Kashmir on Sunday night, the
spokesman added. 
</P>
</TEXT>
