<HEADLINE> Costa Rica, Panama Border Situation Worsens </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
As local radio RPC reported Tuesday , demonstrators of Guabito
sector in Bocas del Toro province, adjoining Costa Rica, have
closed a neighboring road since Monday, challenging authorities
that had ordered the way cleared.
</P>
<P>
