mutiny police shot and killed Carlos Flete, one of the
demonstrators that blocked the road at the border area demanding
its very reestablishment.
</P>
<P>
The so-called "courtesy purchase" was suspended by Costa Rica
several years ago, while Panama did so recently, reciprocally,
which gave place to Panamanian traders' loss of up to 8 million
dollars a year. 
