then have an aggregated equity of 870 million U.S. dollars and a
staff force of 3,500 serving over 390,000 clients throughout the
world.
</P>
<P>
The merger, which is subject to all regulatory and shareholders
' approvals, is expected to become effective by the end of October
this year.  
