<HEADLINE> China Sets Up New Micro-Electronics Lab </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SHANGHAI, July 18 (Xinhua) -- The Infineon-Fudan Lab, jointly
set up by Fudan, a prestigious university based in this east China
metropolis, and Infineon Technology, a German semi-conductor giant,
became operational here today.
</P>
<P>
