<HEADLINE> China's Fund Market Reports Surge </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, July 18 (Xinhua) -- China's securities investment fund
market paced up broadly Tuesday, following the recent corrections.
</P>
<P>
Of the 27 funds, 24 rose and three remained unchanged, which
include two restructured funds. Fund Puhui, the top gainer,
advanced 4.24 percent, according to Homeway, the leading on-line
financial and securities advisory company in China.
</P>
<P>
The Shanghai Stock Exchange Fund Index, which represents 13
