starting point for the upward trend of new funds.
</P>
<P>
The restructured Fund Xingke made its debut on the market
Tuesday, keeping at the ceiling price the whole trading day. Its
trading volume was 1.24 million fund units, and the turnover rate
was 0.55 percent. 
