our multi-media broadcast distribution network, which will help
enable more consumers to view high-quality live video events
throughout the region," said Savio Chow, vice president and
managing director of Yahoo! Asia.
</P>
<P>
PhoenixNet will provide Yahoo! Hong Kong collocation services,
which will facilitate the distribution of broadcast content to
Internet Services Providers through PhoenixNet's satellite network
across Asia Pacific.
</P>
<P>
Yahoo! Hong Kong will provide PhoenixNet with Yahoo! content
and services in English and Chinese for its SpeedCast homepage.
