recent years, a situation which is demonstrated by the
establishment and development of the strategic partnership of
cooperation characterized by equality and trust. Such ties conform
to the fundamental interests of the two countries and their
peoples, and are also conducive to world peace and stability, he
said.
</P>
<P>
