while Angola has sent over Parliament Speaker Roberto de Almeida,
the second highest figure in the country.
</P>
<P>
East Timorese leaders Xanana Gusmao and Jose Ramos Horta are
attending the summit as observers. East Timor is expected to
become the community's 8th member when it achieves full
independence.
</P>
<P>
