<HEADLINE> URGENT: NPC Chairman Meets Russian President </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, July 18 (Xinhua) -- Li Peng, chairman of the Standing
Committee of the Chinese National People's Congress (NPC), met
with visiting Russian President Vladimir Putin at the Great Hall
of the People this afternoon.
</P>
<P>
The meeting is still going on at press time.
</P>
<P>
The two leaders are expected to exchange views on bilateral
relations and international and regional issues of common interest.
</P>
