Tabara of the Czech Republic 7-5, 6-4.
</P>
<P>
Jeff Tarango, the fifth seed from the United States and
finalist at last year's tournament, was ousted by Italian Marzio
Martelli 4-6, 6-2, 6-1.
</P>
<P>
In other matches, Roberto Carretero of Spain defeated Tomas Zib
of the Czech Republic 6-3, 6-2; Juan Antonio Marin of Costa Rica
ousted Hernan Gumy of Argentina 5-7, 6-2, 6-4; Wolfgang Schranz of
Austria beat Alex Lopez Moron of Spain 3-6, 6-2, 7-6.
</P>
<P>
Croatia's Goran Ivanisevic, who initially was to play in the
tournament, withdraew from the event after losing the first round
in Wimbledon. 
