<TEXT>
<P>
LAGOS, July 19 (Xinhua) -- In response to public fears that the
accounts containing alleged loots from public funds by former
Nigerian head of state Sani Abacha might have been moved away or
misused, the Nigerian government Tuesday clarified that they were
still kept "intact".
